{
  "description": "Block Reality 渲染系統索引。包含 Vulkan RT 管線、LOD 優化、後處理效果、天氣與 UI 渲染。所有 client/ 下的類別皆為 CLIENT ONLY。",
  "entries": [
    {
      "id": "render:overview",
      "title": "渲染系統總覽",
      "type": "render",
      "tags": ["render", "vulkan", "client-only", "overview"],
      "content": "Block Reality 採用自訂 Vulkan 渲染管線，包含硬體光追（RT）、ReLAX / NRD 降噪器、DDGI、ReSTIR、LOD、Mesh Shader 等先進技術。所有渲染類別位於 api/client/render/ 與 fastdesign/client/ 下，皆標註 @OnlyIn(Dist.CLIENT)。",
      "metadata": {
        "related_files": [
          "Block Reality/api/src/main/java/com/blockreality/api/client/render/",
          "Block Reality/api/src/main/java/com/blockreality/api/client/rendering/",
          "Block Reality/api/src/main/native/"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "render:BRVulkanRT",
      "title": "BRVulkanRT — Vulkan 光追主控",
      "type": "render",
      "tags": ["render", "vulkan", "rt", "raytracing", "client-only"],
      "content": "BRVulkanRT 是 Vulkan RT 渲染的核心協調器，管理 acceleration structure、ray tracing pipeline、shader binding table。與 BRVulkanDevice、BRClusterBVH、BRReLAXDenoiser 協同。",
      "metadata": {
        "related_files": [
          "Block Reality/api/src/main/java/com/blockreality/api/client/render/rt/BRVulkanRT.java",
