    {
      "id": "render:LOD-optimization",
      "title": "LOD 與地形優化",
      "type": "render",
      "tags": ["render", "lod", "optimization", "client-only"],
      "content": "BRLODEngine、BRSparseVoxelDAG、GreedyMesher、BRMeshletEngine、BRGPUCulling 共同實作多層級細節與剔除。BRDiskLODCache 將遠景 LOD 資料緩存到磁碟。VoxyLODMesher 與 SVDAGLOD3Tracer 提供稀疏體素 LOD 光追。",
